1.title: Sirviendo en el extranjero
1.plot: Nexos, a place where you will find out and learn how to make a difference no matter where you are.

2.title: Dinosaurios y deportes de invierno
2.plot: Enjoy an entertaining afternoon in the snow. Also, we are going to discuss the goal of the talks given at BYU devotionals.

3.title: Sirviendo a la comunidad
3.plot: Today on Nexos, we are going to discuss the importance of teaching our children the language of their parents when they grow up outside of their homeland. Also, we are going to meet to Rocio Mejias, president of the organization "A Helping Hand."

4.title: Celebrando las culturas del mundo

5.title: Bailando alrededor del mundo
5.plot: Today on Nexos, we are going to learn about the culture and traditions of the American Indians. Next, we will take a look at the new car from Lincoln, the "MKZ 2010." Finally, we are going to learn why it is so important to do physical activities outdoors.

7.title: Capoeira
7.plot: Today on Nexos, we will learn about micro-enterprise as well as a particular martial art style known as "Capoeira."

8.title: ROC, Recordando nuestra cultura
8.plot: Today on Nexos, we will discuss all the details of the visit of the Guatemala Ambassador to BYU. Also we will tell you why it is necessary to remember your culture no matter where you are.

9.title: Con la mira en el oro
9.plot: Today, we will enjoy a great ballroom dance. Also, we will discover the new talent of a bilingual singer, and we will discover how fun it is to fly indoors.

imdb.plot outline: Nexos is a weekly program in which young hosts and reporters share stories that are informative, entertaining, and inspiring. Although it's targeted at the youth the content appeals to viewers of all ages. Nexos, staying true to its meaning ("linking"), strives to bring together different cultures as it is broadcast to Latin America in both Spanish and Portuguese.
imdb.title: Nexos
plot: _Nexos_ (qv) is a weekly program in which young hosts and reporters share stories that are informative, entertaining, and inspiring. Although it's targeted at the youth the content appeals to viewers of all ages. _Nexos_ (qv), staying true to its meaning ("linking"), strives to bring together different cultures as it is broadcast to Latin America in both Spanish and Portuguese.
